    In Ce (Type S & D & X)
    edit a file with:
    Col 1
    | 
    V
    -----------------------
    <html><p>
    <body>

    <title>Ce/Ceterm</title>

    <CENTER><H1>Ce/Ceterm Home Page</H1></CENTER>
    <P> 
    <B></B> 
    </B> 
    --------------------------
    Parse it with ^*Home and edit the line begining with 
    <CENTER>.  Run "s/e/aaaaaaa/" on this line.  Make sure the
    colors move as appropriate.  Undo the substitute.  Put the
    cursor on the '<' at the beginning on '</H1>' and type.
    The color should be the same as the preceding word 'Page'.


