    kd F3s    tl; s/^    //; [+1] ke                  # Shift line/region left 4 spaces
    Make sure they work when typed in.  Then back out of ce and go
    back in so they are reloaded from the server.  Make sure they
    still work.  Bug was the second definition did not work when
    loaded from the server.

