    In Ce (Type E)
    1) create a file say "tmp" using "ce tmp".
    2) write some text in the file and write it out to disk.(^w)
       This creates the file tmp.
    3) open another window on the same file.
    4) This second window should be a CC window, but it is NOT.
    5) Write test in first window for file tmp and second instance of tmp.
    6) The last one to write out the file wins.
