    In Ce (Type C) 
    Try the following commands:
    [5,5]    # row 5, column 5
    [5]      # row 5, no change in column (was wrong in 2.1)
    [5,]     # row 5, no change in column
    [+5]     # bump row by 5, no change in column
    [ +5,]   # bump row by 5, no change in column
    [-5]     # decrement row by 5, no change in column
    [ +1 , +1 ] # bump row and column by 1
    [,3]     # current row, column 3
    [,-4]    # current row, go left 4 columns
    [-2,-2]  # go up two rows, go left 2 columns
    []       # do not move cursor
    15       # go to line 15, column 1

