    In ce (Type S)
    the following regular expression
    s/{?*}/   case "@1"/
    Should match from the current cursor position to the end of line
    and put that data in a case statement.

    In ce (Type S)
    execute
    1,$s/@n@n/@n/
    This should compress multiple null lines to half as many lines.
    1,$s/% *@n//
    Every pair of empty lines should become a single null line.
    Every empty line by itself goes away.


